longBusinessSummary: Hotel Fast SSE AB (publ) engages in the franchise and operation of a chain of hotels under the First Hotels brand in Sweden, Norway, and Denmark. It is also involved in the development and lease of properties for hotel operations. The company was formerly known as First Hotels AB (publ) and changed its name to Hotel Fast SSE AB (publ) in February 2025. Hotel Fast SSE AB (publ) was founded in 1993 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
